snippet.title: Strike One - Danny Trejo Action Thriller
snippet.description:
Juan (American Crime’s Johnny Ortiz), a teenager from a gang-controlled neighborhood, is falsely accused of a crime when his is uncle (Danny Trejo, Machete), a former gang leader-- now an actor -- takes him for a joyride that goes wrong. WIthout any money for a lawyer, Juan’s sister turns to a washed up defense attorney to keep Juan out of prison.
